00:44:21.040 --> 00:44:22.870
Lord first. But He said, 'Raise up

00:44:22.880 --> 00:44:25.030
prayer

00:44:25.030 --> 00:44:25.040
groups.'This

00:44:25.040 --> 00:44:28.150
will be birthed out of prayer.

00:44:28.160 --> 00:44:31.270
We must bring back prayer to the church.

00:44:31.280 --> 00:44:33.190
We must have great prayer groups at

00:44:33.200 --> 00:44:35.670
church, not flakiness. We don't get off

