in weirdness where Sister So-and-so and Sister

00:44:37.750 --> 00:44:37.760
So-and-so

00:44:37.760 --> 00:44:39.109
has a gossip

00:44:39.119 --> 00:44:41.670
session the whole time. You have a

00:44:41.680 --> 00:44:44.790
prayer group, not a gossip session. You

00:44:44.800 --> 00:44:46.470
have a prayer group, not a

00:44:46.480 --> 00:44:49.030
potluck.

00:44:49.040 --> 00:44:53.750
I'm talking about carpet-sucking prayer

00:44:53.760 --> 00:44:56.150
where you're on your knees crying out

00:44:56.160 --> 00:44:58.470
for God to move again in this nation

00:44:58.480 --> 00:45:00.950
like we've never seen it before. I'm not

00:45:00.960 --> 00:45:02.390
talking about a prayer group going in

00:45:02.400 --> 00:45:04.470
there and you have a go, 'Well, we're

00:45:04.480 --> 00:45:06.150
praying for her, brother, but

00:45:06.160 --> 00:45:07.750
did you hear about Sister

00:45:07.750 --> 00:45:07.760
So-and-so?

00:45:07.760 --> 00:45:09.430
She's going through this, and

00:45:09.440 --> 00:45:11.829
I heard that her husband is

00:45:11.839 --> 00:45:13.829
not doing too well

00:45:13.829 --> 00:45:13.839
either.'We're

00:45:13.839 --> 00:45:16.150
not there to gossip.

00:45:16.160 --> 00:45:19.270
We're here to pray.

00:45:19.280 --> 00:45:21.030
I don't want to hear about

00:45:21.040 --> 00:45:24.230
your stuff; let's pray.

00:45:24.240 --> 00:45:25.270
I don't want to hear about somebody

00:45:25.280 --> 00:45:28.470
else's business either.

00:45:28.480 --> 00:45:29.750
Do you understand what I'm

00:45:29.760 --> 00:45:31.589
saying? That's what the Lord is putting

00:45:31.599 --> 00:45:33.109
