00:45:33.119 --> 00:45:35.430
groups.

00:45:35.440 --> 00:45:37.750
All these major revivals were birthed out

00:45:37.760 --> 00:45:40.630
of prayer, and we've got to fill this

00:45:40.640 --> 00:45:42.630
with prayer

00:45:42.640 --> 00:45:45.190
for what's about to happen. And I saw

00:45:45.200 --> 00:45:48.150
Branson having a major revival. I want

00:45:48.160 --> 00:45:49.910
to be a part of wherever it's going to

00:45:49.920 --> 00:45:51.190
be. I know it's going to be in

00:45:51.200 --> 00:45:53.109
Collinsville. I know it's going to be in

00:45:53.119 --> 00:45:54.870
there. So you want to have

00:45:54.880 --> 00:45:56.710
two places so you can experience it both

00:45:56.720 --> 00:45:59.430
times. I just

00:45:59.440 --> 00:46:01.990
want my feet in the river.

00:46:02.000 --> 00:46:04.950
Whatever it takes.

00:46:04.960 --> 00:46:06.710
I want to be a part of prayer. I want to

00:46:06.720 --> 00:46:09.030
be a part of this great outpouring

00:46:09.040 --> 00:46:11.030
of the Spirit of God like we've never

00:46:11.040 --> 00:46:13.589
seen before. Do you understand? And I

00:46:13.599 --> 00:46:15.910
know that it's going to take some

00:46:15.920 --> 00:46:18.870
effort to get there. We've got

00:46:18.880 --> 00:46:22.230
to wake up.

00:46:22.240 --> 00:46:24.069
He's taking the lid off the septic and

00:46:24.079 --> 00:46:25.750
he's sucking it out and cleaning

00:46:25.760 --> 00:46:29.990
things up. Do you all understand?

00:46:30.000 --> 00:46:31.750
I hope you all understand the

00:46:31.760 --> 00:46:34.630
urgency of the hour. It's time to wake

00:46:34.640 --> 00:46:36.150
up

00:46:36.160 --> 00:46:40.950
in 2026. You're going to wake up.

00:46:40.960 --> 00:46:45.829
Then I was taken to

00:46:45.839 --> 00:46:50.870
Asia and I saw a massive ball glowing

00:46:50.880 --> 00:46:55.270
in Japan. I saw it highlighted

00:46:55.270 --> 00:46:55.280
with—it

00:46:55.280 --> 00:46:59.190
looked to me

00:46:59.200 --> 00:47:02.630
like platinum, the way platinum looks,

00:47:02.640 --> 00:47:05.510
like if you were to see transparent platinum

00:47:05.520 --> 00:47:08.790
where it's

00:47:08.800 --> 00:47:13.030
not solid-looking but

00:47:13.040 --> 00:47:16.630
it has a transparency to it like the

00:47:16.640 --> 00:47:18.950
streets of gold in heaven, but it was

00:47:18.960 --> 00:47:22.550
platinum. It was outlining Japan. And as

00:47:22.560 --> 00:47:24.630
it was outlined, it split down the

00:47:24.640 --> 00:47:27.030
middle with a major earthquake. It had

00:47:27.040 --> 00:47:30.630
a dome of a ball, a sphere that

00:47:30.640 --> 00:47:33.030
was cut in half.

00:47:33.040 --> 00:47:36.550
And as it was glowing, it had some kind

00:47:36.550 --> 00:47:36.560
of—that

00:47:36.560 --> 00:47:40.470
platinum had light shining from

00:47:40.480 --> 00:47:44.069
the inside out that

00:47:44.079 --> 00:47:46.710
was so piercing that it looked

00:47:46.720 --> 00:47:48.550
like something out of some kind—it

00:47:48.550 --> 00:47:48.560
was

00:47:48.560 --> 00:47:51.750
half of a sun, but it was a

00:47:51.760 --> 00:47:54.150
platinum color. It wasn't yellow like

00:47:54.160 --> 00:47:57.190
the sun; it was like a platinum color

00:47:57.200 --> 00:48:00.309
like fire. It was like a light and it

00:48:00.319 --> 00:48:03.750
was shining out of Japan. But as I was

00:48:03.760 --> 00:48:07.109
looking and I gazed upon North Korea, I

00:48:07.119 --> 00:48:09.990
saw the people praying

00:48:10.000 --> 00:48:13.829
in their homes and they were singing but

00:48:13.839 --> 00:48:17.109
they had no words. They were not allowed

00:48:17.119 --> 00:48:20.790
to sing out loud in fear of their life.

00:48:20.800 --> 00:48:23.430
So they were worshipping God with hand

00:48:23.440 --> 00:48:25.190
gestures

00:48:25.200 --> 00:48:28.950
and doing like this for praise,

00:48:28.960 --> 00:48:30.870
and they were shaking their hands and

00:48:30.880 --> 00:48:33.430
they were singing with just their lips

00:48:33.440 --> 00:48:35.910
moving with no sound and they were

00:48:35.910 --> 00:48:35.920
worshipping

00:48:35.920 --> 00:48:39.030
our Father. And I saw

00:48:39.030 --> 00:48:39.040
them—they

00:48:39.040 --> 00:48:41.349
were so cold as they were

00:48:41.349 --> 00:48:41.359
worshipping

00:48:41.359 --> 00:48:43.910
the Lord.

00:48:43.910 --> 00:48:43.920
Their

00:48:43.920 --> 00:48:45.990
skin was kind of

00:48:45.990 --> 00:48:46.000
light-colored

00:48:46.000 --> 00:48:48.150
because the cold was so

00:48:48.160 --> 00:48:51.990
cold in their homes—these

00:48:51.990 --> 00:48:52.000
Christians—but

00:48:52.000 --> 00:48:53.829
they were scared to make any loud

00:48:53.839 --> 00:48:55.589
noise because they were in there with

00:48:55.599 --> 00:48:58.150
their family and they were just

00:48:58.150 --> 00:48:58.160
worshipping

00:48:58.160 --> 00:49:02.150
with their hands.

00:49:02.160 --> 00:49:05.510
It made me want to weep because I saw all

00:49:05.520 --> 00:49:07.190
over

00:49:07.200 --> 00:49:08.790
and they had their hands and they were

00:49:08.800 --> 00:49:11.109
moving their fingers like this and they

00:49:11.119 --> 00:49:13.030
were doing it and they were smiling as

00:49:13.040 --> 00:49:15.430
big as they could. Their faces

00:49:15.440 --> 00:49:17.910
were glowing with joy

00:49:17.910 --> 00:49:17.920
worshipping

00:49:17.920 --> 00:49:24.950
our Father with no noise.

00:49:24.960 --> 00:49:28.790
I saw God take the

00:49:28.800 --> 00:49:32.470
Chinese flag. I saw the old

00:49:32.480 --> 00:49:35.190
communistic with the stars and the

00:49:35.200 --> 00:49:37.670
old

00:49:37.680 --> 00:49:38.390
flag.

00:49:38.400 --> 00:49:39.030
It's

00:49:39.030 --> 00:49:39.040
the

00:49:39.040 --> 00:49:40.710
China flag.

00:49:40.720 --> 00:49:44.470
I saw Him take their flag and He wadded

00:49:44.480 --> 00:49:47.750
it up in a ball with His fist and it was

00:49:47.760 --> 00:49:50.309
all crinkled up. That flag right there,

00:49:50.319 --> 00:49:52.950
He crinkled it up and He wadded it up

00:49:52.960 --> 00:49:55.270
like a ball. His fist was like

00:49:55.280 --> 00:49:57.430
this, but His hand was full of the flag.

00:49:57.440 --> 00:50:00.950
But I could see the stars and the red

00:50:00.960 --> 00:50:02.630
crinkling out of His hand. So I could

00:50:02.640 --> 00:50:04.549
see He was wrinkling it up like He was

00:50:04.559 --> 00:50:06.630
angry at it.

00:50:06.640 --> 00:50:08.630
All of a sudden, it was attached to

00:50:08.640 --> 00:50:11.589
North Korea.

00:50:11.599 --> 00:50:14.230
I was interceding and the Lord said,

00:50:14.240 --> 00:50:17.750
'They will entertain angels unaware.

00:50:17.760 --> 00:50:19.670
For if you can't get in, I'll let you

00:50:19.680 --> 00:50:21.670
in.'That's

00:50:21.680 --> 00:50:23.510
what He said. 'If they

00:50:23.520 --> 00:50:26.950
won't let you in through the border, I

00:50:26.960 --> 00:50:28.309
will let you in through my

00:50:30.054 --> 00:50:30.064
