00:50:47.440 --> 00:50:50.150
to another, and they were all like a

00:50:50.150 --> 00:50:50.160
superhighway

00:50:50.160 --> 00:50:54.309
above our atmosphere.

00:50:54.319 --> 00:50:58.230
There were lights of all kinds of colors

00:50:58.240 --> 00:51:01.109
coming through these tubes. It was

00:51:01.119 --> 00:51:03.030
almost like when you go to a bank and

00:51:03.040 --> 00:51:05.270
you send it out in the

00:51:05.280 --> 00:51:06.950
drive-thru and you put that in there and

00:51:06.960 --> 00:51:08.790
you push the button and the tube

00:51:08.790 --> 00:51:08.800
gets—the

00:51:08.800 --> 00:51:10.390
little thing gets—you put your money

00:51:10.400 --> 00:51:11.910
