00:51:17.520 --> 00:51:20.790
went from America to Asia to

00:51:20.800 --> 00:51:22.790
other parts of South America, and there

00:51:22.800 --> 00:51:25.190
was a superhighway above us in the

00:51:25.200 --> 00:51:26.870
heavenlies.

00:51:26.880 --> 00:51:29.349
I don't know what I was seeing. There

00:51:29.349 --> 00:51:29.359
were

00:51:29.359 --> 00:51:33.829
purples and pinks, blues—all that

00:51:33.839 --> 00:51:36.150
