00:51:36.160 --> 00:51:37.829
And there was no darkness in

00:51:37.839 --> 00:51:40.549
it. The tubes

00:51:40.559 --> 00:51:43.430
were lit up with light,

00:51:43.440 --> 00:51:45.670
all of them. But they were the

00:51:45.680 --> 00:51:49.910
size of what a human body would be.

00:51:49.920 --> 00:51:51.829
And it looked like spaghetti noodles

00:51:51.839 --> 00:51:54.870
all over the place.

00:51:54.880 --> 00:51:57.510
A superhighway all over the place. And

00:51:57.520 --> 00:51:59.430
it was like you would take one

00:51:59.440 --> 00:52:03.109
of those pickup sticks. That's how

00:52:03.119 --> 00:52:04.870
