00:52:07.440 --> 00:52:09.750
The pickup sticks.

00:52:09.760 --> 00:52:10.710
Does anybody know what I'm talking

00:52:10.720 --> 00:52:13.430
about? The pickup sticks, the game, like

00:52:13.440 --> 00:52:15.349
