00:54:12.000 --> 00:54:14.790
But it was like a

00:54:14.800 --> 00:54:16.390
witness somehow. I don't know how, like

00:54:16.400 --> 00:54:18.870
you're there and you're

00:54:18.880 --> 00:54:20.470
traveling around. Maybe you won't go

00:54:20.480 --> 00:54:21.990
into someone's house in North Korea and

00:54:22.000 --> 00:54:23.910
film them and say, "I want to

00:54:23.920 --> 00:54:25.750
video you and have

00:54:25.750 --> 00:54:25.760
ministry."I'm

00:54:25.760 --> 00:54:27.910
not trying to

00:54:27.920 --> 00:54:29.670
be flaky with this; this is how the

00:54:29.680 --> 00:54:31.510
Lord showed me, folks. You know what I'm

00:54:31.520 --> 00:54:33.829
saying? And it was translating

00:54:33.839 --> 00:54:35.829
all over the place. It was not just

00:54:35.839 --> 00:54:38.470
one place; it was all in South America.

00:54:38.480 --> 00:54:41.510
I saw it translating. I saw—am I

00:54:41.520 --> 00:54:42.870
using the word

00:54:42.870 --> 00:54:42.880
right?—translate,

00:54:42.880 --> 00:54:47.190
to go all over the place,

00:54:47.200 --> 00:54:48.790
and the glory of the

00:54:48.800 --> 00:54:51.990
Lord showed up.

00:54:52.000 --> 00:54:53.589
Healings, demonstrations, and

00:54:53.599 --> 00:54:55.030
manifestations like you wouldn't

00:54:55.040 --> 00:54:56.630
believe;

00:54:56.640 --> 00:54:59.349
I'm telling you, souls are coming

00:54:59.359 --> 00:55:01.829
