00:55:32.400 --> 00:55:34.470
interpretation.

00:55:34.480 --> 00:55:36.230
You're saying transport.

00:55:37.680 --> 00:55:40.390
Transport through language, no language

00:55:40.400 --> 00:55:43.670
barriers. You'll know North

00:55:43.680 --> 00:55:46.790
Korea, you'll know whatever, and

00:55:46.800 --> 00:55:48.470
you'll be able to just talk to them and

00:55:48.480 --> 00:55:49.910
they'll be able to talk to you.

00:55:49.920 --> 00:55:51.750
There will be a supernatural on

00:55:51.760 --> 00:55:53.750
your mind.

00:55:53.760 --> 00:55:56.950
I saw working with the angelic host. The

00:55:56.960 --> 00:55:58.150
Lord said, "You will work with the

00:55:58.160 --> 00:55:59.990
angels.

00:56:00.000 --> 00:56:01.750
You'll work with the angels in the

00:56:01.760 --> 00:56:05.349
days ahead as a

00:56:05.349 --> 00:56:05.359
sign."He

00:56:05.359 --> 00:56:07.190
said, "I don't want any should

00:56:07.200 --> 00:56:09.990
perish, Brandon, but when this gospel is

00:56:10.000 --> 00:56:11.589
preached as a witness into all the

00:56:11.599 --> 00:56:13.349
