He was ginormous. He had a totally black

01:07:39.200 --> 01:07:40.789
outfit on, which I don't

01:07:40.789 --> 01:07:40.799
understand—that's

01:07:40.799 --> 01:07:42.309
what it looked like,

01:07:42.319 --> 01:07:45.109
some kind of weird

01:07:45.119 --> 01:07:48.549
garment. But the other was a

01:07:48.559 --> 01:07:51.270
Roman soldier that had Roman garb on

01:07:51.280 --> 01:07:53.910
like you would see in the movies.

01:07:53.920 --> 01:07:57.270
And I saw them take the cat o'nine tails

01:07:57.280 --> 01:08:00.470
and one whipped this side and the other

01:08:00.480 --> 01:08:04.549
one whipped this side. And as I saw that

01:08:04.559 --> 01:08:08.069
