01:08:08.079 --> 01:08:11.190
His body and it was excruciating.

01:08:11.200 --> 01:08:13.270
It was dripping

01:08:13.280 --> 01:08:16.309
from His body—the bone, everything.

01:08:16.319 --> 01:08:18.950
It was the most grotesque

01:08:18.960 --> 01:08:22.229
thing I've ever seen.

01:08:22.239 --> 01:08:25.269
I saw the crown of

01:08:25.279 --> 01:08:27.510
thorns upon His head pressed down and

01:08:27.520 --> 01:08:29.829
blood was running down His forehead. His

01:08:29.839 --> 01:08:31.829
beard was missing pieces

01:08:31.839 --> 01:08:33.669
where they had ripped the

01:08:33.679 --> 01:08:37.189
beard out of His face.

01:08:37.199 --> 01:08:39.749
I remember I was standing over here as I

01:08:39.759 --> 01:08:41.749
was watching this happen and I was

01:08:41.759 --> 01:08:44.070
weeping and I was screaming but

01:08:44.080 --> 01:08:47.192
nobody could hear me and I said, "Stop! You must

01:08:47.192 --> 01:08:47.202
stop!"and I was

01:08:47.202 --> 01:08:47.990
screaming

01:08:49.920 --> 01:08:51.910
because they were beating Him

01:08:51.920 --> 01:08:53.510
with those whips. They were

01:08:53.520 --> 01:08:55.269
whipping His body and His

01:08:55.279 --> 01:08:58.789
body would tremble as they

01:08:58.799 --> 01:09:00.789
were whipping His body and

01:09:00.799 --> 01:09:03.430
the blood was so much on the ground

01:09:03.440 --> 01:09:05.189
it was like He was in a pool of

01:09:05.199 --> 01:09:10.149
blood.

01:09:10.159 --> 01:09:14.229
As they did it, I saw Jesus look up

01:09:14.239 --> 01:09:16.550
and I saw Him, out of His mouth, tell that

01:09:16.560 --> 01:09:19.990
one soldier, "I love you.

01:09:20.000 --> 01:09:24.870
I love

01:09:24.870 --> 01:09:24.880
you."I

01:09:24.880 --> 01:09:27.749
saw it. His face looked up at

01:09:27.759 --> 01:09:30.550
him and it was the

01:09:30.560 --> 01:09:33.990
most sincere look in His eyes as they were

01:09:34.000 --> 01:09:40.950
laughing and they were beating His body.

01:09:40.960 --> 01:09:43.349
Jesus was standing beside me over here as I

01:09:43.359 --> 01:09:45.110
watched this all happen. I can even

01:09:45.120 --> 01:09:46.550
tell you what His back looked like

01:09:46.560 --> 01:09:48.709
before they beat Him.

01:09:48.719 --> 01:09:50.309
He was not skinny looking; He was

01:09:50.319 --> 01:09:53.030
muscular looking. His skin looked olive.

01:09:53.040 --> 01:09:55.590
It looked glossy

01:09:55.600 --> 01:09:58.390
from oily sweat.

01:09:58.400 --> 01:10:01.270
You know how whenever you sweat and you

01:10:01.280 --> 01:10:03.910
get that oil on your body from not

01:10:03.920 --> 01:10:06.709
having a bath in a little bit? That's

01:10:06.719 --> 01:10:08.630
the way His back looked before they

01:10:08.640 --> 01:10:16.709
began. I watched it.

01:10:16.719 --> 01:10:18.790
The Lord spoke to me that day and He

01:10:18.800 --> 01:10:21.590
said to me,

01:10:21.600 --> 01:10:24.390
"What do you not understand

01:10:24.400 --> 01:10:27.110
