01:10:27.120 --> 01:10:30.470
healed,'Brandon?

01:10:30.480 --> 01:10:34.470
What do you not understand about

01:10:34.470 --> 01:10:34.480
this?"He

01:10:34.480 --> 01:10:37.750
said, "If somebody was to tell you

01:10:37.760 --> 01:10:41.750
that you weren't saved,

01:10:41.760 --> 01:10:45.350
