01:10:51.840 --> 01:10:54.229
am saved.

01:10:54.239 --> 01:10:56.709
I am delivered.

01:10:56.719 --> 01:10:59.350
I know He saved my soul by what He did

01:10:59.360 --> 01:11:02.070
for

01:11:02.070 --> 01:11:02.080
me.'"But

01:11:02.080 --> 01:11:03.830
the moment you feel sickness and

01:11:03.840 --> 01:11:07.990
disease, you doubt

01:11:08.000 --> 01:11:11.110
