01:11:14.320 --> 01:11:16.550
to get healed

01:11:16.560 --> 01:11:18.390
is the same faith that it takes to be

01:11:18.400 --> 01:11:22.149
saved. They're the

01:11:22.149 --> 01:11:22.159
same."He

01:11:22.159 --> 01:11:24.070
said,

01:11:30.080 --> 01:11:32.229
"You don't realize what it takes for you

01:11:32.239 --> 01:11:35.830
to say, 'I was once lost, but now I'm

01:11:35.840 --> 01:11:39.270
