01:11:43.520 --> 01:11:45.430
don't look at the miracle that

01:11:45.440 --> 01:11:48.229
truly is.

01:11:48.239 --> 01:11:50.630
But the same faith that you would fight

01:11:50.640 --> 01:11:52.630
somebody

01:11:52.640 --> 01:11:55.750
by telling them, 'I know I'm

01:11:55.750 --> 01:11:55.760
saved.'"They

01:11:55.760 --> 01:11:57.189
say, "No, I don't believe it. You

01:11:57.199 --> 01:11:58.950
still act the way you used to sometimes.

01:11:58.960 --> 01:12:00.870
