01:12:26.630 --> 01:12:26.640
on.'But

01:12:26.640 --> 01:12:28.630
it's the same way the pain

01:12:28.640 --> 01:12:31.110
of the soul is whenever you

01:12:31.110 --> 01:12:31.120
are

01:12:31.120 --> 01:12:32.390
