01:12:32.400 --> 01:12:33.750
but you don't question your mind because

01:12:33.760 --> 01:12:36.310
of the symptom of it. I'm saved. I

01:12:36.310 --> 01:12:36.320
believe.

01:12:36.320 --> 01:12:38.229
I'm once saved, always saved.

01:12:38.239 --> 01:12:39.350
Don't you know that? Well, I'm once

01:12:39.360 --> 01:12:41.910
healed, always healed.

01:12:41.920 --> 01:12:44.709
I'm healed and whole and well. By His

01:12:44.719 --> 01:12:48.310
