01:13:11.360 --> 01:13:13.430
Christ has redeemed me from the curse of

01:13:13.440 --> 01:13:17.669
the law.

01:13:17.679 --> 01:13:19.350
Deuteronomy 28 says there are a lot of

01:13:19.360 --> 01:13:21.430
curses there at the very end

01:13:21.440 --> 01:13:25.430
