01:13:57.760 --> 01:14:00.149
But you must believe that I'm a healer

01:14:00.159 --> 01:14:02.790
just as much as I'm a redeemer.

01:14:02.800 --> 01:14:05.430
I take you out of hell. I've

01:14:05.440 --> 01:14:06.950
