01:14:13.440 --> 01:14:16.470
shook me.

01:14:16.480 --> 01:14:18.950
Oh, I don't believe that, Brandon. It's

01:14:18.960 --> 01:14:22.550
what I saw. It's what I experienced

01:14:22.560 --> 01:14:27.830
