01:14:33.360 --> 01:14:35.990
I couldn't control myself because of

01:14:36.000 --> 01:14:41.270
what I saw Jesus go through.

01:14:41.280 --> 01:14:44.390
Jesus paid the price for you to walk in

01:14:44.400 --> 01:14:47.430
victory over mental torment.

01:14:47.440 --> 01:14:49.669
Jesus paid the price for you to walk in

01:14:49.679 --> 01:14:53.030
victory over depression, over anxiety,

01:14:53.040 --> 01:14:56.310
over fear, over all the things that the

01:14:56.320 --> 01:14:58.870
devil tries to. Don't accept

01:14:58.880 --> 01:15:01.669
