01:15:13.760 --> 01:15:15.990
Shut the door to the devil and run and

01:15:16.000 --> 01:15:20.390
say, 'I'm not taking your

01:15:20.390 --> 01:15:20.400
package.'Symptoms

01:15:20.400 --> 01:15:23.270
come and people die. I

01:15:23.280 --> 01:15:25.830
understand that. I've seen it. But I try

01:15:25.840 --> 01:15:27.510
to get a hold of it just like that for

01:15:27.520 --> 01:15:30.470
my daughter Megan. I'm walking it out

01:15:30.480 --> 01:15:33.030
