Jesus Christ is the same yesterday,

01:16:05.840 --> 01:16:09.977
today, and forever,

01:16:14.000 --> 01:16:18.070
and I choose to believe it.

01:16:18.080 --> 01:16:20.790
I choose to believe it.

01:16:20.800 --> 01:16:23.030
But if you're here tonight and you've

