01:16:47.520 --> 01:16:51.510
You need to accept Jesus Christ

01:16:51.510 --> 01:16:51.520
tonight.'If

01:16:51.520 --> 01:16:53.910
you're here and you've never

01:16:53.920 --> 01:16:55.510
accepted Him, if you've never asked

01:16:55.520 --> 01:16:57.270
Jesus Christ to be your Lord and

01:16:57.280 --> 01:16:59.350
personal Savior, He died and

