So, I'm going to say it right now. Say,

01:20:08.400 --> 01:20:09.910
'Jesus,

01:20:09.920 --> 01:20:12.550
I believe You're the Son of God. I

01:20:12.560 --> 01:20:13.990
believe that You died for me and You

01:20:14.000 --> 01:20:17.110
