01:40:45.360 --> 01:40:47.430
coming from heaven

01:40:47.440 --> 01:40:50.070
and going through this

01:40:50.080 --> 01:40:54.709
valley of death.

01:40:59.119 --> 01:41:03.270
He has a long, flowing robe on.

01:41:03.270 --> 01:41:03.280
There

01:41:03.280 --> 01:41:05.270
are

01:41:05.280 --> 01:41:06.790
little

01:41:09.119 --> 01:41:12.390
wear holes at the

01:41:12.400 --> 01:41:13.990
bottom where it

01:41:14.000 --> 01:41:16.550
brushes against the dirt on the

01:41:16.560 --> 01:41:19.109
ground

01:41:19.109 --> 01:41:19.119
by

01:41:19.119 --> 01:41:20.950
his

01:41:20.960 --> 01:41:22.870
sandals.

01:41:25.440 --> 01:41:28.790
This is an

01:41:28.800 --> 01:41:33.350
old prophetic man.

01:41:33.360 --> 01:41:49.350
Can these bones live?

01:42:43.520 --> 01:42:46.390
Behind

01:42:46.390 --> 01:42:46.400
him

01:42:46.400 --> 01:42:49.510
is a massive tree

01:42:49.520 --> 01:42:51.910
built into the

01:42:51.920 --> 01:42:55.350
rock, and

01:42:55.360 --> 01:42:57.750
a waterfall

01:43:03.280 --> 01:43:05.830
has just started to

01:43:05.840 --> 01:43:07.590
erupt off that cliff. The

01:43:07.590 --> 01:43:07.600
water is

01:43:07.600 --> 01:43:11.510
flowing down into

01:43:11.510 --> 01:43:11.520
the

01:43:11.520 --> 01:43:15.189
valley from the tree. It's a massive

01:43:15.199 --> 01:43:17.590
tree, so big you couldn't

01:43:17.600 --> 01:43:20.709
put your arms around it. It is

01:43:20.719 --> 01:43:22.790
beautiful, green, and alive,

01:43:22.800 --> 01:43:24.870
like a redwood in

01:43:24.880 --> 01:43:27.750
California;

01:43:30.320 --> 01:43:32.709
you could

01:43:32.719 --> 01:43:35.189
drive a car through it.

01:43:37.360 --> 01:43:40.149
It's planted in the rock, and the water

01:43:40.159 --> 01:43:42.870
is running out of the tree, coming down

01:43:42.880 --> 01:43:44.550
the side of the mountain where the man

01:43:44.560 --> 01:43:57.830
is standing and blowing his horn.

01:45:40.480 --> 01:45:44.470
Now I see two lungs

01:45:44.480 --> 01:45:47.350
attached outside of

01:45:47.360 --> 01:45:49.830
a body,

01:45:49.840 --> 01:45:52.310
breathing in that

01:45:52.320 --> 01:45:55.830
water.

01:45:55.840 --> 01:45:58.390
These

01:45:58.400 --> 01:46:00.790
lungs are

01:46:00.800 --> 01:46:02.390
positioned right underneath that

01:46:02.400 --> 01:46:04.550
waterfall, and

01:46:04.560 --> 01:46:07.109
I can see

01:46:07.119 --> 01:46:10.310
life coming into

01:46:10.310 --> 01:46:10.320
them.

01:46:10.320 --> 01:46:12.709
I can see the blood flow and the veins,

01:46:12.719 --> 01:46:15.030
and

01:46:15.040 --> 01:46:17.510
they

01:46:17.520 --> 01:46:54.950
are sparkling.

01:46:54.960 --> 01:46:57.189
Why would it be

01:46:57.199 --> 01:47:00.310
lungs? Lord, what is that? Why are

01:47:00.320 --> 01:47:01.830
the lungs breathing like that outside

01:47:01.840 --> 01:47:12.870
the body?

01:47:54.320 --> 01:47:59.430
The man just sat down on the rock.

01:47:59.440 --> 01:48:02.310
He went from blowing a horn to sitting

01:48:02.320 --> 01:48:04.950
down to look at the valley,

01:48:04.960 --> 01:48:14.229
and the water is flowing right by him.

01:48:14.239 --> 01:48:16.790
He's sitting crisscross,

01:48:20.719 --> 01:48:22.390
looking out

01:48:22.400 --> 01:48:27.189
over the edge.

01:48:27.199 --> 01:48:44.790
Why is he sitting down now?

01:48:44.800 --> 01:48:47.270
We're seated with him

01:48:54.960 --> 01:48:57.590
in the heavenlies, far above all

01:48:57.600 --> 01:48:59.910
principalities.

01:48:59.920 --> 01:49:02.310
It's a place of authority

01:49:02.310 --> 01:49:02.320
and

01:49:02.320 --> 01:49:05.510
rest.

01:49:05.520 --> 01:49:10.149
You're not

01:49:21.840 --> 01:49:23.350
toiling,

01:49:23.360 --> 01:49:24.709
walking around,

01:49:24.709 --> 01:49:24.719
or

01:49:24.719 --> 01:49:27.830
pacing. I'm seated because I'm firm

01:49:27.840 --> 01:49:32.310
in Him and resting.

01:49:32.320 --> 01:49:36.390
That man is taking a

01:49:36.400 --> 01:49:40.310
seat, looking out over the edge

01:49:40.320 --> 01:49:44.070
in complete peace,

01:49:44.080 --> 01:49:46.550
watching the water flow over the people.

01:49:46.560 --> 01:49:48.790
He did what he

01:49:48.790 --> 01:49:48.800
was

01:49:48.800 --> 01:49:51.030
supposed to do; he blew his horn and he

01:49:51.030 --> 01:49:51.040
sat

01:49:51.040 --> 01:49:52.950
down.

01:51:48.960 --> 01:51:52.149
It's a

01:51:53.679 --> 01:51:57.430
place of rest. Trust

01:51:57.440 --> 01:52:01.830
confidently in Me.

01:53:16.320 --> 01:53:21.830
I see a peach seed.

01:53:40.639 --> 01:53:42.149
Everything in the kingdom is about

01:53:42.159 --> 01:53:43.910
seeds:

01:53:43.920 --> 01:53:46.070
planting the seed and believing for the

01:53:46.080 --> 01:53:48.709
harvest.

01:53:58.400 --> 01:54:00.629
Let the Word come into you as a

01:54:00.639 --> 01:54:04.070
seed and it springs forth life.

01:54:13.360 --> 01:54:17.189
Everything revolves around a seed.

01:54:17.199 --> 01:54:19.910
Seed is life,

01:54:19.920 --> 01:54:21.750
but you have to plant the seed to reap

01:54:21.760 --> 01:54:24.149
the harvest.

01:54:24.159 --> 01:54:26.870
The Word doesn't return void.

01:54:26.880 --> 01:54:28.709
You're planting the seed of the Word

01:54:28.719 --> 01:54:30.790
inside your heart, and it springs forth

01:54:30.800 --> 01:54:33.830
life.

01:54:42.719 --> 01:54:43.669
What was interesting

01:54:43.679 --> 01:54:48.390
is the seed was covered by blood.

01:54:48.400 --> 01:54:50.550
I could see the peach seed covered in

01:54:50.560 --> 01:54:56.790
blood

01:55:04.560 --> 01:55:07.030
as you take your seat.

01:55:13.119 --> 01:55:16.070
It was a split fruit, and

01:55:20.960 --> 01:55:25.510
the peach seed looked red.

01:55:25.520 --> 01:55:27.910
The Lord said, 'It's covered

01:55:27.920 --> 01:55:30.629
in the blood.'You

01:55:30.629 --> 01:55:30.639
sow

01:55:30.639 --> 01:55:33.830
the seed, and I reap the

01:55:33.840 --> 01:55:35.430
harvest.

01:55:35.440 --> 01:55:37.990
Life is in the Word.

01:55:40.719 --> 01:55:48.870
Seedtime

01:55:51.840 --> 01:55:54.070
and harvest never cease.

01:55:54.080 --> 01:55:56.070
Whatsoever a man sows, that will he also

01:55:56.080 --> 01:55:59.270
reap. As long as the earth remains, there

01:55:59.270 --> 01:55:59.280
is seedtime

01:55:59.280 --> 01:56:03.030
and harvest.

01:56:03.040 --> 01:56:06.070
I believe that's in First Peter, right?

01:56:11.119 --> 01:56:13.750
The flowers wither

01:56:13.760 --> 01:56:16.149
and the grass

01:56:18.950 --> 01:56:18.960
fades,

01:56:20.800 --> 01:56:22.870
but the Word of

01:56:22.880 --> 01:56:35.669
the Lord will remain forever.

01:58:24.639 --> 01:58:27.030
Thank You, Father, for the blood that

01:58:27.030 --> 01:58:27.040
covers

01:58:27.040 --> 01:58:29.030
every seed.

01:58:29.040 --> 01:58:31.990
The seeds we

01:58:31.990 --> 01:58:32.000
sowed

01:58:32.000 --> 01:58:34.310
in the past have come to harvest

01:58:34.320 --> 01:58:38.149
at last. Genesis 8:22

01:58:38.159 --> 01:58:40.950
says

01:58:45.270 --> 01:58:45.280
that

01:58:46.639 --> 01:58:48.870
as long as the earth

01:58:48.880 --> 01:58:51.510
remains, there will be

01:58:51.520 --> 01:58:53.830
planting and harvest, cold and heat, summer and winter,

01:58:53.840 --> 01:58:56.870
day and night;

01:59:13.589 --> 01:59:13.599
they

01:59:29.360 --> 01:59:33.030
shall not cease.

01:59:33.040 --> 01:59:35.830
I thank You, Father, for seedtime and

01:59:35.840 --> 01:59:38.229
harvest tonight.

01:59:46.000 --> 01:59:47.510
We ask for a crop failure

01:59:47.520 --> 01:59:49.669
over the bad

01:59:51.360 --> 01:59:53.510
seeds we sowed

01:59:53.520 --> 01:59:55.350
ignorantly or willingly.

01:59:55.360 --> 01:59:58.790
We repent and call

01:59:58.790 --> 01:59:58.800
for

01:59:58.800 --> 02:00:01.270
repentance over those bad seeds,

02:00:01.280 --> 02:00:03.189
and I thank You, Lord, that

02:00:03.189 --> 02:00:03.199
they

02:00:03.199 --> 02:00:05.910
will not bear fruit in our life. We call

02:00:05.920 --> 02:00:09.189
for

02:00:09.199 --> 02:00:12.629
crop failure over the bad seeds, and

02:00:12.639 --> 02:00:14.470
we thank You that the good seeds

02:00:14.480 --> 02:00:18.390
bring forth a thirty, sixty, and hundredfold return in

02:00:18.400 --> 02:00:21.750
the name of Jesus.

02:00:21.760 --> 02:00:25.910
We call for every bad seed we have sowed

02:00:25.920 --> 02:00:29.430
to have a crop failure in Jesus'name. We

02:00:29.440 --> 02:00:32.470
call forth abundance to the extreme

02:00:32.480 --> 02:00:38.709
that overflows over the good seeds

02:00:38.719 --> 02:00:40.790
and over the man. Father, the position

02:00:40.800 --> 02:00:43.350
of the elder with the long

02:00:43.350 --> 02:00:43.360
beard—Father,

02:00:43.360 --> 02:00:46.390
we take our seat.

02:00:48.960 --> 02:00:50.310
Can these bones live?

02:00:50.320 --> 02:00:53.430
Can these bones live?

02:01:24.960 --> 02:01:26.790
We stay in that place of our

02:01:26.800 --> 02:01:31.109
authority and we take our seat.

02:01:31.119 --> 02:01:34.310
We take our rest. We come up higher. And

02:01:34.320 --> 02:01:38.070
we thank you that you have our best

02:01:38.080 --> 02:01:41.109
in mind, best in heart,

02:01:41.119 --> 02:01:54.310
Abba.

02:01:54.320 --> 02:02:00.950
We thank you, Lord. We thank you, Lord.

02:02:00.960 --> 02:02:07.669
That's interesting. Now, I see a fox.

02:02:07.679 --> 02:02:10.790
He's looking to the man on the

02:02:10.800 --> 02:02:14.149
rock.

02:02:14.159 --> 02:02:17.830
The fox is down below in the valley. The

02:02:17.840 --> 02:02:21.350
fox is looking slyly up toward the man on

02:02:21.360 --> 02:02:23.189
the rock.

02:02:23.199 --> 02:02:25.910
He has a long bushy tail with a white

02:02:25.920 --> 02:02:30.149
tip

02:02:30.159 --> 02:02:32.629
and he's looking up. He has a black

02:02:32.639 --> 02:02:36.870
coal nose, black little

02:02:36.880 --> 02:02:39.669
coal eyes, and his head is

02:02:39.679 --> 02:02:42.390
toward the ground. But then he looked up

02:02:42.400 --> 02:02:47.514
at the man sitting on the rock, the fox.

02:03:11.040 --> 02:03:15.750
I see a baby bassinet

02:03:15.760 --> 02:03:19.270
on wheels. It looks like a baby buggy,

02:03:19.280 --> 02:03:22.070
but on the side where the baby

02:03:22.070 --> 02:03:22.080
is,

02:03:22.080 --> 02:03:25.189
it's an

02:03:25.189 --> 02:03:25.199
old-school

02:03:25.199 --> 02:03:28.790
1900s baby bassinet that has

02:03:28.800 --> 02:03:31.510
an umbrella over the

02:03:31.520 --> 02:03:35.910
baby. I see a white baby gown, white

02:03:35.920 --> 02:03:40.229
blankets, and all this beautiful

02:03:40.239 --> 02:03:43.430
white color, and the white is glowing.

02:03:43.440 --> 02:03:46.390
There's a gold

02:03:46.400 --> 02:03:49.669
trim around the

02:03:49.669 --> 02:03:49.679
baby basket.

02:03:49.679 --> 02:03:52.629
It's open, but

02:03:52.639 --> 02:03:54.950
all the trim at the edge of

02:03:54.960 --> 02:03:57.750
the baby bassinet is gold and it's

02:03:57.760 --> 02:04:01.669
braided.

02:04:01.679 --> 02:04:04.310
It's welded; it's all meshed

02:04:04.320 --> 02:04:06.870
together. So it's seamless,

02:04:06.880 --> 02:04:09.189
but it's all like

02:04:09.199 --> 02:04:11.270
little slits all on it like this. And it's

02:04:11.280 --> 02:04:14.229
gold. There

02:04:14.229 --> 02:04:14.239
are

02:04:14.239 --> 02:04:16.950
strips of gold going down on

02:04:16.960 --> 02:04:19.430
this bassinet.

02:04:44.080 --> 02:04:47.381
I see a glorious figure that

02:04:47.381 --> 02:04:47.391
has

02:04:47.391 --> 02:04:48.149
no face—a

02:04:48.149 --> 02:04:48.159
being

02:04:48.159 --> 02:04:50.950
that has no face,

02:04:50.960 --> 02:04:53.990
that

02:04:54.000 --> 02:04:57.430
has a beautiful

02:04:57.440 --> 02:05:00.709
sparkling gown that's watching over the

02:05:00.719 --> 02:05:12.149
baby.

02:05:18.960 --> 02:05:28.390
It looks like a veil baby,

02:05:28.400 --> 02:05:30.149
but he's leaning over looking at the

02:05:30.159 --> 02:05:34.390
baby with no face and he has a sparkling

02:05:34.400 --> 02:05:55.109
gown.

02:06:24.880 --> 02:06:45.430
So the stone is stone.

02:06:45.440 --> 02:06:47.830
We're clothed in His

02:06:47.840 --> 02:06:50.390
glory. Come to Him as a

02:06:50.400 --> 02:06:54.069
child.

02:06:54.079 --> 02:07:02.310
Come to Him as the baby.

02:07:02.320 --> 02:07:04.709
A baby needs all its needs met by the

02:07:04.719 --> 02:07:07.750
father or the mother.

02:07:07.760 --> 02:07:10.870
It cannot meet its own needs.

02:07:10.880 --> 02:07:14.149
It's really helpless.

02:07:14.159 --> 02:07:15.750
It's sitting there laying in

02:07:15.760 --> 02:07:17.669
that bassinet and the father's

02:07:17.679 --> 02:07:21.430
just doting over his baby.

02:07:21.440 --> 02:07:25.750
The father—the faceless one

02:07:25.750 --> 02:07:25.760
in glory—is

02:07:25.760 --> 02:07:29.270
doting over that

02:07:29.280 --> 02:07:33.990
baby, looking over that child. And

02:07:34.000 --> 02:07:35.830
the baby's just cooing and

02:07:37.360 --> 02:07:40.629
kicking its little legs,

02:07:40.639 --> 02:07:42.550
little toes. And the

02:07:42.560 --> 02:07:44.550
daddy's just there. I could see the

02:07:44.560 --> 02:07:47.750
glorious thing—I want to say it's

02:07:47.750 --> 02:07:47.760
the

02:07:47.760 --> 02:07:50.069
Lord, I don't

02:07:50.069 --> 02:07:50.079
know—looking

02:07:50.079 --> 02:07:53.430
at this baby and the baby's

02:07:53.440 --> 02:07:55.030
just kicking.

02:07:56.719 --> 02:08:00.310
I can feel the presence.

02:08:00.320 --> 02:08:02.870
He's watching over me. He's watching

02:08:02.880 --> 02:08:09.669
over you or His babies or His children.

02:08:09.679 --> 02:08:16.870
What's that fox doing?

02:08:55.920 --> 02:08:57.669
That's so interesting. That is really

02:08:57.679 --> 02:09:19.189
beautiful.

02:09:19.199 --> 02:09:23.189
We love you, Lord.

02:09:23.199 --> 02:09:25.350
We come to you.

02:09:25.360 --> 02:09:28.069
We're seated with you in

02:09:28.079 --> 02:09:30.470
the heavenlies, like that old man. But

02:09:30.480 --> 02:09:34.790
we come as babies before the Great I

02:09:34.790 --> 02:09:34.800
Am—not

02:09:34.800 --> 02:09:40.069
as adults, but as your babies.

02:09:40.079 --> 02:09:45.430
And we're away from that fox.

02:09:45.440 --> 02:09:48.470
We thank you, Lord.

02:09:48.480 --> 02:09:51.830
We thank you, Father, for that peace

02:09:51.840 --> 02:09:55.189
as we sit at your feet

02:09:55.199 --> 02:09:58.149
for the peace

02:09:58.159 --> 02:10:01.189
that passes understanding.

02:10:01.199 --> 02:10:04.629
The peace that

02:10:04.639 --> 02:10:29.990
passes all understanding.

02:10:30.000 --> 02:10:36.390
We thank you, Lord. We thank you, Lord.

02:10:36.400 --> 02:10:43.830
Hallelujah.

02:12:50.960 --> 02:12:54.470
I see there was a very steep hill for

02:12:54.480 --> 02:12:58.550
more of you to climb.

02:13:02.079 --> 02:13:05.189
I see a steep hill. And the climb has

02:13:05.199 --> 02:13:10.310
been very intense.

02:13:10.320 --> 02:13:13.669
Push, push, push.

02:13:13.679 --> 02:13:16.950
Climb,

02:13:16.960 --> 02:13:18.950
climb, climb.

02:13:40.400 --> 02:13:43.430
It's been a

02:13:43.440 --> 02:13:46.229
long, long road for some of you. But the

02:13:46.229 --> 02:13:46.239
breakthrough—the

02:13:46.239 --> 02:13:49.589
long, long road. You

02:13:49.599 --> 02:13:50.709
feel like you've been climbing,

02:13:50.719 --> 02:13:52.790
climbing, climbing. 'Where are we going

02:13:52.800 --> 02:13:54.790
to get to the

02:14:31.350 --> 02:14:31.360
summit?'It's

02:15:02.880 --> 02:15:05.189
all about breaking

02:15:05.199 --> 02:15:08.870
through for you. You've been climbing.

02:15:08.880 --> 02:15:11.350
You're at that place of rest.

02:15:11.360 --> 02:15:14.790
Your baby is speaking to the dry bones

02:15:14.800 --> 02:15:19.270
of your life. 'Can these bones

02:15:19.270 --> 02:15:19.280
live?'Of

02:15:19.280 --> 02:15:21.430
your circumstances, of many you have

02:15:21.440 --> 02:15:24.229
given up on. But I hear the Spirit of the

02:15:24.239 --> 02:15:26.870
Lord say, 'I'm bringing forth life to

02:15:26.880 --> 02:15:29.350
your circumstances

02:15:29.360 --> 02:15:31.430
where it seemed the valley of your

02:15:31.440 --> 02:15:34.470
dry bones were dead and that you are in

02:15:34.480 --> 02:15:37.189
the

02:15:37.189 --> 02:15:37.199
valley.'But

02:15:37.199 --> 02:15:40.149
the water's here. The birthing

02:15:40.159 --> 02:15:42.790
is here. The

02:15:42.800 --> 02:15:50.069
baby is here.

02:15:50.079 --> 02:15:54.470
It's the time of the seed

02:15:54.480 --> 02:15:57.030
that you sowed in the past; you're going

02:15:57.040 --> 02:15:59.669
to reap the harvest at last.

02:15:59.679 --> 02:16:01.189
Speaking to what you thought was

02:16:01.199 --> 02:16:03.830
dormant.

02:16:03.840 --> 02:16:05.589
You climb, you climb,

02:16:05.599 --> 02:16:07.990
you climb. I see the people

02:16:07.990 --> 02:16:08.000
getting

02:16:08.000 --> 02:16:10.310
weary in well-doing. You

02:16:10.320 --> 02:16:12.149
don't see the manifestation of what you

02:16:12.159 --> 02:16:14.310
believe for

02:16:14.320 --> 02:16:17.589
day after day. You

02:16:17.599 --> 02:16:21.430
feel weary in

02:16:21.430 --> 02:16:21.440
well-doing.

02:16:21.440 --> 02:16:24.470
But when you let go of the rope and you

02:16:24.480 --> 02:16:27.030
let God—'I'm sitting down, Lord. I'm

02:16:27.040 --> 02:16:30.629
just taking my

